      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a strong luster, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains very reliable and drives smoothly, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great.",
