    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 B32 power plant, complete with individual throttle bodies and a fully operational double-VANOS system. This example has undergone critical subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. Recent technical updates include a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a cooling system refresh utilizing a high-efficiency aluminum radiator. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced steering feedback. A performance-ready chassis with a clean power band and excellent throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
