    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical of careful road use. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with substantial tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seats are supple and clean, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, navigation system, and premium audio, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and there are no warning lights on the dashboard. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for by an owner who values longevity. It comes with two sets of keys and a folder of service receipts for your peace of mind.",
